	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That would be the Namco 118 mapper, which is effectively a subset of the MMC3 (appears to lack IRQs and SRAM support, perhaps complex PRG/CHR 'flipping' as well).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


